data.description: This spacious 4BR/2BA home with 3-car garages located on +/- 2.5 Acres with beautiful mature trees in the Oak West Subdivision is such a treasure!    Relax on the wrap-around porch and then come inside.   This home features an open-concept floor plan with gorgeous trim work detail and lots of natural lighting.   The kitchen with so many special touches has quartz countertops, tons of storage, an island, and is open to the breakfast area and dry bar that includes a bar area for sitting.  The dining room, just off the kitchen is spacious with a beautiful bay window and is open to the cozy living room with a wood-burning fireplace, tray ceiling, fabulous shadow box trim wall molding, and a built-in for your books and art with closed storage cabinets too.  The primary suite is nice and roomy with a pretty tray ceiling and a bathroom with dual sinks and closets, a soaking tub, a separate shower, and a floor-to-ceiling cabinet.  The other 3 bedrooms each have a beautiful window nook for sitting and one has a large closet with a work bench area for all your crafts and projects. There are also stairs that lead to a 1300 sqft decked attic that could be transformed into extra living space.   The backyard has endless possibilities!  There is room for your pets, to put in a pool, outdoor grill, storage shop, and a garden too!  Dine under the breezeway and relax with Family and Friends on the back deck.  Park your RV, boat, and other toys too! Schedule your showing today!  Enjoy our 3D tour feature and walk through the home using your device.
